graph LR
    subgraph ZKFC [ZooKeeper Failover Controller Daemon]
        HM[Health Monitor]
        ASE[Active Standby Elector]
    end

    subgraph LocalNameNode [Local NameNode Host]
        NN[NameNode Process]
    end

    subgraph ZooKeeperCluster [ZooKeeper Cluster]
        ZK[ZooKeeper Quorum]
    end

    HM -->|1. Poll Health via HAServiceProtocol RPC| NN
    HM -->|2. Report State Changes| ASE
    ASE <-->|3. Create/Watch Ephemeral Lock ZNode| ZK
    ASE -->|4. Trigger State Transition RPC (Active/Standby)| NN
